Eye of the Warmaster										CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General.Fighter.BattleMind	PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Combat Expertise								PRESTAT:1,INT=13	PRETOTALAB:6																												DESC:You watch an opponent in battle, analyzing his maneuvers, tactics, and stance to learn his combat style. Once you have broken down a foe's methods, you can present him with tactics that defeat his style.																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.44
Resolve of the Steel Mind									CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:General.Fighter.BattleMind																PRESTAT:1,INT=13	PRETOTALAB:3																												DESC:You are always ready for combat. You use a series of exercises, intense training, and mental focus to create a combat routine that allows you to reliably respond to any threat.																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.44
